Metadata.Title: The Perfect Doctor Chapter 6
Metadata.Description:
After 47 exposed what the hospital was doing, the hospital fired 47 and banned 47 forever.
But it's time to put an end to it
 Wipe the virus completely, make sure all close contacts are injected with the blocking agent 
Eliminate all doctors and executive with direct data, and make sure the virus doesn't reappear在47曝光了医院的所作所为后，医院开除了47，并且永远禁止47进入。
但是时候结束这一切了
彻底抹除病毒，保证密集接触者都被注射阻断药剂
消灭所有拥有直接数据的医生和主管，保证病毒不会再出现

Exit: Snowmobile
